Today is 16th september,
=> HTML Head
- The <head> element is contain metadata and it's placed between <html> and <body> tag.
- Metadata define are HTML document title,charset,style,link,script and other meta information.
- <title>, <style>, <meta>, <link>, <script>, and <base> these all tag are describe as metadata.

