=> HTML Layout
- There are four different ways to create multicolum layout 1)HTML Table, 2)CSS framework, 3)CSS Float property, 4)CSS Flexbox.
- Table tag was not designed to be a layout tool.
- If you want to create your layout fast, you can use CSS framework.
- Float property is easy to learn, you just need remember hoe it's work..
- Flexbox is a new layout mode in CSS 3.

